title: ARAM Q
body:
Hey was just wondering why my ARAM q times have gotten so long all of a sudden?
I am only lvl 27 on this account and usually wait "at least" 10min and even upwards of 20min.
Whats with that?

replies.body: nobody plays aram unless its past midnight and they have nothing to do, that's why
i know that not many ppl play aram but i have been playing for years and never had this problem b4
